uake catalog information in regions that currently have no\ntraditional networks. With an expanding MyShake network, we expect the event\ndetection capabilities to improve and provide useful data on seismicity and\nhazards.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 22 Apr 2019 07:31:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-09-18"}
