es the platform, the requester cannot make a higher\nprofit by setting different quality requirements for different tasks.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 22 Apr 2019 12:05:56 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 25 Apr 2019 01:48:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-04-26"}
