arly universe and study the evolution of potential in a toy model of universe\ncomposed only by RRG.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 22 Apr 2019 14:40:57 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 30 May 2019 22:19:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-06-25"}
